>> "README.md" echo( ^|---------^|----------^|-------------^|
>> "README.md" echo( ^| GET ^| `/api/config/settings/ticket-threshold` ^| Lire le seuil actuel ^|
>> "README.md" echo( ^| PUT ^| `/api/config/settings/ticket-threshold` ^| Modifier (body: `{"threshold": 0.7}`) ^|
>> "README.md" echo( ^| GET ^| `/api/config/settings` ^| Tous les parametres systeme ^|
>> "README.md" echo( 
